04:27.350 --> 04:27.910
Lu Yan!

04:30.230 --> 04:30.830
Lu Yan!

04:35.570 --> 04:36.180
Lu Yan!

04:40.430 --> 04:40.990
Lu Yan!

04:42.520 --> 04:43.150
Lu Yan!

06:06.610 --> 06:07.930
